issue.title: Shared grooves, synced mixing
Integrations
issue.body:
I'm thinking it might be cool to do integrations in the future. Perhaps Ableton and FL Studio integrations that allow you to export straight to the software...

Just thinking slack-like I guess, but it would be really great.

issue.title: Make Master Channels Sliders affect  in relation to the track current sliders
issue.body:
For example, if I have a track on half volume, and I want to simply turn the master volume down a bit,

the child track's volume should move down into relation to the master track, and not simply be the same as master volume

this can be done similar to how I implemented the initVolume for allowing a volume of zero at song playback
